videos.description: Trent Forrest drives into the lane and sends a pass to the rim for Christ Koumadje, who rises up for the big two-handed finish.
videos.headline: Forrest lobs to Koumadje for alley-oop jam

videos.description: Tre Jones catches Phil Cofer sleeping and knocks the ball away before taking it all the way to the rim for the fast-break finish.
videos.headline: Jones picks Cofer's pocket for easy bucket

videos.description: Cam Reddish drives baseline and takes off for the rim, eluding Mfiondu Kabengele and flipping in a reverse off the glass.
videos.headline: Reddish flies in for acrobatic reverse layup

videos.description: Zion Williamson spins his way to the rim and tries to finish inside, but Mfiondu Kabengele swats it away.
videos.headline: Kabengele stuffs Zion at the rim

videos.description: M.J. Walker can't finish the finger roll, but Phil Cofer grabs the rebound and cleans up the miss with a rim-rocking two-handed flush.
videos.headline: Cofer hammers down putback slam

videos.description: Zion Williamson gets the rebound and sends a laser down the court to Tre Jones, who finishes with the reverse.
videos.headline: Zion rips cross-court pass to Jones for finish

videos.description: Zion Williamson tries to drive to the basket, but Trent Forrest pokes him in the eye and causes him to exit the game.
videos.headline: Zion leaves game after getting poked in eye

videos.description: Terance Mann swings it to the corner for PJ Savoy, who sinks the 3-pointer to give Florida State a 39-38 lead over Duke at the half.
videos.headline: Savoy hits go-ahead triple before halftime

videos.description: Terance Mann finds Christ Koumadje for the alley-oop on the first play of the 2nd half, then M.J. Walker finds him again just a minute later.
videos.headline: Koumadje starts 2nd half with two alley-oop jams

videos.description: Terance Mann finds Mfiondu Kabengele for the alley-oop flush, but RJ Barrett comes right back with a monster jam of his own over Mfiondu Kabengele.
videos.headline: Barrett answers Kabengele's alley-oop with posterizing slam

videos.description: M.J. Walker misses the runner, but Phil Cofer comes flying in to clean up the miss with a strong two-handed slam.
videos.headline: FSU takes lead on Cofer's putback dunk

videos.description: PJ Savoy draws the foul on Cam Reddish, then knocks down two out of three free throws to give the Seminoles a 78-76 lead in the final seconds.
videos.headline: Savoy draws foul, hits go-ahead FTs late

videos.description: RJ Barrett missed the game-tying free throw with five seconds left but Mfiondu Kabengele deflects it out of bounds to give Duke one more chance after a razor-thin replay review.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (The controversial call that set up Duke's game-winner) 2019/01/12 ESHEET

videos.headline: The controversial call that set up Duke's game-winner

videos.description: Zion Williamson leaves late in the first half with an eye injury, but Cam Reddish's last-second 3-pointer propels Duke past Florida State 80-78.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCB Highlight (Duke overcomes Zion injury to beat FSU in wild finish) 2019/1/12 ESHEET

videos.headline: Duke overcomes Zion injury to beat FSU in wild finish
